ia Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Legendary dividend stock <strong>Middlesex Water</strong> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/MSEX\" title=\"Middlesex Water Company\">MSEX</a></span>) has been pummeled in recent weeks. The stock made a new relative high in early November, only to move from $70 to $55 in virtually a straight line. Does that make the</p>", "image": null, "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745348-middlesex-water-this-dividend-king-is-not-worth-your-time", "pub_date": "2024-12-19 18:56:01"}, {"id": "4745365", "title": "December Fed Takeaway: A Foggier Outlook And A More Cautious Path", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/172717098/image_172717098.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"US Federal Reserve, Washington DC (in winter)\" data-id=\"172717098\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1028px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/172717098/image_172717098.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/172717098/image_172717098.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/172717098/image_172717098.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/172717098/image_172717098.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/172717098/image_172717098.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/172717098/image_172717098.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/172717098/image_172717098.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/172717098/image_172717098.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">uschools</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>The Federal Reserve delivered another 25-basis point (bp) cut to its policy rate in December, but paired this decision with revisions to its economic projections that imply reemerging concerns around inflation risks and relative confidence in the labor market. As a result, after lowering</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/172717098/image_172717098.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745365-december-fed-takeaway-foggier-outlook-more-cautious-path", "pub_date": "2024-12-19 18:50:00"}, {"id": "4745343", "title": "The Delusion Of The Tesla Robotaxi And Its Excessive Valuation", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1181076506/image_1181076506.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Businessman Wondering How Low It Can Go\" data-id=\"1181076506\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1132px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1181076506/image_1181076506.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1181076506/image_1181076506.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1181076506/image_1181076506.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1181076506/image_1181076506.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1181076506/image_1181076506.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1181076506/image_1181076506.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_i