n/s3/uploads/getty_images/1466744580/image_1466744580.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1466744580/image_1466744580.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1466744580/image_1466744580.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1466744580/image_1466744580.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\">Tap water running into a kitchen sink.</p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Liudmila Chernetska</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>In life and investing, consistency matters greatly. This is because wealth and success rarely come quickly. Even if it did, it's going to take commitment and dedication to maintain and build on that success.</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1466744580/image_1466744580.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745342-american-water-works-time-to-buy-this-water-utility-now", "pub_date": "2024-12-19 18:38:29"}, {"id": "4745340", "title": "Viridian: Positive Chronic TED Data Likely To Lead To BLA Filing In Second Half Of 2025 (Rating Upgrade)", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2177969613/image_2177969613.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"A fertility lab technician meticulously performs the fertilization of an egg.\" data-id=\"2177969613\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1025px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2177969613/image_2177969613.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2177969613/image_2177969613.jpg?io=getty-c-