{"id": "4745339", "title": "Stocks Have Swung From Overbought To Oversold Seemingly Overnight", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157394864/image_157394864.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Crash in financial crisis\" data-id=\"157394864\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"2832px\" height=\"2035px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157394864/image_157394864.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157394864/image_157394864.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157394864/image_157394864.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157394864/image_157394864.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157394864/image_157394864.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157394864/image_157394864.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157394864/image_157394864.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157394864/image_157394864.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Bartolome Ozonas</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>The broad market has been pulling back since the beginning of December from an overbought technical condition. With that process well underway, if not near completion, as I suggested yesterday, the only fundamental concern on investors' minds seemed to be the final Fed</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157394864/image_157394864.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745339-stocks-have-swung-from-overbought-to-oversold-seemingly-overnight", "pub_date": "2024-12-19 18:23:03"}]}